WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.500
Dr. McCarthy, he refuses to say anything.

00:03.500 --> 00:07.000
He's too dangerous.

00:07.000 --> 00:09.000
Stay back. I know what I'm doing.

00:14.000 --> 00:18.000
Please, help me.

00:19.000 --> 00:21.500
Ten years ago, my little brother was bitten

00:21.500 --> 00:24.000
by a vampire. I've never seen him since.

00:24.000 --> 00:25.500
That's why I decided to learn everything

00:25.500 --> 00:27.000
about him.

00:27.000 --> 00:28.500
If I set you free, you'll tell me where my

00:28.500 --> 00:30.000
brother is.

00:35.000 --> 00:39.000
Sweetie, you should have listened to them.

